{"tid":806392,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"好心絕體絕命都市咪再出啦","createTime":"2018-09-04T15:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-26T11:03:22.000Z","uid":1121,"like":54,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c35b2ab824e3e8d7f3c2a72284ebe194d6a82b37","tid":806392,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:31:32.000Z","msg":"出親日本都奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c79f655dc519435a94f8814ab36406912f7612","tid":806392,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:34:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>推特話題《絕體絕命都市4》熊本地震之後會不會引發歷史重演？</strong><br />\n<br />\n最近日本發生的熊本地震實在是相當不幸的天災，不過影響方面從目前看來並沒有像311東日本地震那樣嚴重，應該算是不幸中的大幸了....而因為地震的關係，最近在推特上面有人想起了一款遊戲跟這兩件事情都有關係，就是曾經一度發售延期、終止開發的《絕體絕命都市4》。<br />\n<br />\n過去因為東日本大地震的關係，原本預計發售的《絕體絕命都市4》在震災過後發表「自主規制」，遊戲不但無限期延期，後來更是宣布終止開發，遊戲面臨結束的命運。<br />\n<br />\n後來事隔多年，版權從原開發商Irem移轉到Granzella，由原本的遊戲開發團隊繼續製作，並且舊系列重新上架。<br />\n不過現在在遊戲發售之前，發生的熊本地震又讓玩家擔心：「會不會歷史又再度重演？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/233429_f0cc9a572909d919ae4359381742872d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F233429_f0cc9a572909d919ae4359381742872d.png&h=f07d608f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/233430_46e8b30b5480f39dbf16bc0a61eb1ec1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F233430_46e8b30b5480f39dbf16bc0a61eb1ec1.png&h=add2d61e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"29bbf7cf3fd09c350d416f63fc2a261ffea13fa1","tid":806392,"uid":1121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:35:47.000Z","msg":"其實現在網路上面也有一些玩家正在討論這件事情，認為有可能會因為「自主規制」而延期的聲音是有的，但也有許多玩家認為，正是因為發生地震災害，更是應該讓遊戲發售。<br />\n<br />\n部分玩家認為，遊戲裡面的災害說明其實相當有用，裡面的知識與狀況都有專人監修，在發生震災的時候，或許可以救人一命，從遊戲中學習知識的效果通常吸收的也比較快。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/233515_6a7e7c03d4fc1ccc21c9ab7c5b3f756d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F233515_6a7e7c03d4fc1ccc21c9ab7c5b3f756d.png&h=0a3f0ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/233532_5b1a5e4a24283b47b0b52bc288d6d786.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F233532_5b1a5e4a24283b47b0b52bc288d6d786.png&h=d862e89e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因此目前也有許多應援遊戲發售的聲音，認為就是因為發生了地震，更是要將遊戲推出。不過說到底，新公司就是為了要讓遊戲復活才取得版權的，作法應該會跟過去有所不同才對？<br />\n<br />\n不過這也是一種微妙的運氣很差啊....遊戲好不容易宣告復活，現在當年讓遊戲腰斬的原因又再出現一次，相信誰也不希望發生地震吧（嘆）<br />\n地震發生本身就是一個相當不幸的天災了，不只是「絕體」這款遊戲，很多創作相關的「不謹慎」問題可能最近又會被拿出來討論了，在自肅方面相當嚴謹的日本來說各種意義上都是很辛苦啊～"},{"pid":"1013c172f642e81a7632323c5982cd1ddd9df6ea","tid":806392,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b38822b2bf97de5b67554d136384ecabb88982","tid":806392,"uid":33539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"2011福島個獲又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8f52139b0febe3e7e9abdecba2912db51f7d9e","tid":806392,"uid":8565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:10:18.000Z","msg":"今次出唔出到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57acf42a2d77c55c2bfaa3a25cf6aa2d5619b0db","tid":806392,"uid":6018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201